    • openOnlyForVehicleClasses

      TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem.ChangeLaneState openOnlyForVehicleClasses(VehicleClass... allowVehicleClasses)
      Opens the lane for a given set of vehicle classes. All other classes are prohibited to drive on this lane further on.

    • closeOnlyForVehicleClasses

      TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem.ChangeLaneState closeOnlyForVehicleClasses(VehicleClass... allowVehicleClasses)
      Closes the lane for a given set of vehicle classes. All other classes are allowed to drive on this lane further on.
